name: SlipGlow
description: The Hum enables illumination. Connection through light, sound, vision; shared dreams, dark imaginings. Focus deeply, you'll find that time, place, all sense of being, becomes meaningless, slips away. It is at this point that you become truly free. Interfusion with those who were, those who are, and those who are yet to materialise within this world, is within reach. You just have to step into the light with me...
